 substantial agency in terms of what plot to choose and crops to cultivate.
 The trade-off is that it will become harder to compare plot level outcomes
 (eg fertilizer use on the plot on which the soil test was done versus control).
 At the same time, there are now also interesting household level outcomes
 that we can investigate, such as crops cultivated.
\end_layout

